summary: Hey if you’re taking request at the moment, can you write about Harry being with a singer/rapper and she is going to be deported...
question: Hey if you’re taking request at the moment, can you write about Harry being with a singer/rapper and she is going to be deported (Mexico) just like the situation from 21 savage. Thank you!
answer:
Hello my love,

Before I say anything else I just want to say that I’m flattered you sent this into me and that you felt I had the capability to translate something like this for you. I’ve not been doing this writing thing as long as others on here have and I’ve been overwhelmed by the reaction.

I will always, always try to complete a request that gets sent in because I appreciate a challenge, however on this occasion I don’t think it’s possible for me to do so.

I stressed really hard last night to try and come up with even a vague idea for it, but there are a few reasons why I have to say I can’t complete it.

Firstly, I don’t know anything about 21 Savage, or the situation you’ve asked me to write about, and whilst it’s easy for me to research it, there’s so many other elements surrounding him that would compromise other parts of the piece. I hadn’t even heard of him until you sent in this, so he is completely alien to me.

Secondly, your request is so specific and perhaps a little too controversial for this particular site. Again, I know very little about that part of the world, and I could spend hours doing research about the whole thing and not be completely satisfied at the end of it. I have to be so, so careful with how I write the reader because people from all walks of life read these pieces. I desperately try and avoid describing the reader’s physical features at all times because I see so much about it on here. I get scared writing Also, I am absolutely terrified of saying something that’s not 100% correct or accurate, because knowing how this site can be, people will call me out on it if I make a mistake.

I really really hope you can understand where I’m coming from, and I hope it doesn’t discourage you from reading my work in the future.

Kate xxx
